    "attributes": {
        "action": "Implement Tier 3 visa scheme which is currently suspended",
        "additional_details": "To remove the current labour shortages in the UK which are leading to businesses closing and empty shops!",
        "background": "The most simple way to address the immediate labour shortage would be for the Government to turn Tier 3 visas (for unskilled workers) back on. This would allow Europeans to be sponsored by employers to work in the UK. Quickly we would have our essential workers back including HGV drivers",
